divs: Sighting DetailsDid not see this object. But believe no one would see an object traveling at this speed during daytime. May be meteor or space junk, but think anything large enough to make a hole in the clouds and moving this fast would have caused some damage when it hit the ground.
Summary: Took photo at 250th of second. Did not see until downloaded on computer.
